Package io.github.thebusybiscuit.slimefun4.implementation.items.electric.machines

package io.github.thebusybiscuit.slimefun4.implementation.items.electric.machines
This package contains the different implementations of SlimefunItem that are also an EnergyNetComponent with the type CONSUMER. Machines do not generate power, they consume it.
